                        <interp inst="t18560514-520-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 36.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the jury,—
<rs id="t18560514-520-punishment-27" type="punishmentDescription">
